OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early morning cloud will
OL,6,Fquickly clear during the morning to
OL,7,Fleave largely sunny skies. Some fair
OL,8,Fweather cloud will develop come the
OL,9,Fafternoon, but it will remain dry
OL,10,Fthroughout. Feeling very warm with
OL,11,Flighter winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine and sunny evening will
OL,14,Flead to a largely clear night. Patchy
OL,15,Fmist and cloud however will move into
OL,16,Feastern parts later. A warm night,
OL,17,Fespecially in urban areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
