OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,6,Fonce any early morning low cloud and
OL,7,Fmist clears. Feeling very warm,
OL,8,Fespecially in the strong sunshine.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FStaying dry and settled throughout the
OL,12,Frest of the week and into the weekend.
OL,13,FRemaining very warm initially but
OL,14,Ffeeling a little cooler by Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
